        title: `<div class="container-fluid aboutUSZ  mb-3"> <div class="row contentfixer "> <p class="aboutUS">ABOUT US</p> </div> </div> <div class="container-fluid contentfixer mb-5"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-6 col-12"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-6 col-6"> <i class="lni lni-cool"></i> <div class="plannerAbout"> <h4>Activities</h4> Ladakh is full of advantarous & activities around play and experiance. </div> </div> <div class="col-md-6 col-6"> <i class="lni lni-travel"></i> <div class="plannerAbout"> <h4>Travel Arrangements</h4> We can plan challenges and advantarous trip across Ladakh. </div> </div> </div> <div class="row mt-3"> <div class="col-md-6 col-6"> <i class="lni lni-cog"></i> <div class="plannerAbout"> <h4>Private Guide</h4> We also customize the packages as you want to experiance </div> </div> <div class="col-md-6 col-6"> <i class="lni lni-map"></i> <div class="plannerAbout"> <h4>Location Manager</h4> we make sure to provide tips and helpful guide to tourist across Ladakh </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-6 col-12 fixemob2"> <h4>It's time to start your adventure</h4> <p class="masterParabaout">In the heart of Ladakh's rugged beauty lies a landscape adorned with the world's highest motorable passes and serene lakes like Pangong and Tso Moriri. Traverse the challenging Manali-Leh and Srinagar-Leh Highways during the summer, turning the journey into an exhilarating adventure. Ladakh's cultural tapestry, woven with monasteries like Diskit and vibrant festivals, offers a deep dive into Tibetan Buddhism. As the stars illuminate the high-altitude heavens, Ladakh's stark beauty transforms into a mesmerizing celestial theater for stargazers. </p> <p class="masterParabaout">Amidst the warm hospitality of the locals and encounters with resilient wildlife, Ladakh unfolds as a destination that not only challenges the adventurer but also captivates the soul with its unique blend of nature and culture.</p> <button class="viewAboutDest" onclick="showPage('packages')">View Destination</button> </div> </div> </div>`,
        content: `   <div class="container-fluid pesonaKabber mt-2 mb-2"> <div class="row contentfixer"> <div class="col-md-6 col-12 justify-content-center align-content-center "> <img src="./assets/artist-white.jpg" alt="" width="300"> <h6 class="mt-4">Mr.Angchuk</h6> </div> <div class="col-md-6 col-12"> <p class="detislPerson"> Roar through high mountain passes on our specially designed tour bikes, conquering challenging terrains that offer breathtaking views at every turn. Strap on your boots for thrilling treks through ancient monasteries, hidden valleys, and pristine lakes, guided by experienced locals who unveil Ladakh's best-kept secrets. As night falls, lose yourself under Ladakh's star-studded canvas during our sky-gazing extravaganza, a celestial dance that adds a magical touch to your expedition. <br><br> This isn't just a trip; it's a chance to connect with global adventurers, share stories around the campfire, and build friendships that transcend borders. Get ready for an offbeat adventure where every moment is a highlight, every road a revelation, and every day an opportunity for unforgettable experiences in Ladakh's breathtaking embrace. </p> <div class="desconnect"> <div class="soclialsNet d-flex"> <div class="col-2"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/hiddenvalleyhomestay?utm_source=qr&igsh=MW5qd2traDkzeTcyeA==" target="_blank" class="fabLink" ><i class="lni lni-instagram"></i></a></div> <div class="col-2"> <a href="" target="_blank" class="fabLink" ><i class="lni lni-whatsapp"></i> </a></div> </div> <div class="cfet mt-3"> <span class="malller" onclick="shareContent()">support@ladakhthrill.com</span> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>        `,
